high_descs: Turn right, walk around the silver counter to the right, take a right at the fridge and walk to the silver counter on the right.
Pick up the dirty black plate from the left side of the counter.
Turn right, hang a left at the fridge and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the plate inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn left, hang a left at the stove and walk to the rack of wooden shelves ahead.
Put the rinsed plate on the middle shelf on the right side of the rack.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed plate on a shelf.

high_descs: walk around to the other side of the counter
pick up the plate sitting on the counter
turn right and cross the kitchen to the sink
put the plate in the sink and wash the plate and then pick it up from the sink
turn around and cross the kitchen to the shelves against the wall
place the plate on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: wash the plate and put it away

high_descs: Turn right and walk around the table to the opposite side with the stools next to it. Face the table.
Pick up the dirty gray plate on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the plate in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the stove, then turn left and walk to the shelving unit in the corner of the room, on the right side.
Place the plate to the right of the dirty plate.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean plate on a shelf.
